    "body" : "<p>PHPMyAdmin ticks <code>`</code> the names of the tables to allow for strangely named tables. That probably will fix the problem you're having</p>\n<pre><code>String sql=&quot;SELECT a.ACode, b.BCod \n FROM (b RIGHT JOIN c ON b.BCod = c.CCod) \n      INNER JOIN a ON c.`à` = a.ID \n WHERE b.CodComm=&quot;+code;\n</code></pre>\n"
